If you're familiar with Vimperator, just put gvimail.js in [VIMPERATOR]/plugin, and gvimail.css in [VIMPERATOR]/colors, where [VIMPERATOR] is ~/.vimperator or %HOMEPATH%\vimperator. Edit the file to see if you can customize.

If you're not familiar with Vimperator, read the pages 
http://code.google.com/p/gvimail/ ,
http://code.google.com/p/gvimail/wiki/Installation and 
http://vimperator.mozdev.org to know what to do.

Post issues to 
http://code.google.com/p/gvimail/issues/list
or mail it to me (dotmg/at/users.sourceforge.net)

Happy GViMail-ing.
